history.content: I wanted to confirm the enrollment status for CS 160. When I search for it on "Search for classes" from CalCentral, it shows the status as "Waitlist." But when I click on the class for further details, it says its closed. But it also says that the wait list total is 156 and the wait list capacity is 225, so I thought that would mean the class is still accepting people to the waitlist. Could you confirm whether its closed or accepting people onto the waitlist?
history.subject: Enrollment Status for CS160 (UI Design)
